{"tid":439672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重口味公園】日本有個「多肥西公園」？究竟搞邊科？","createTime":"2017-10-18T04:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T07:35:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9618cd437d3d5a84d0d2260617070c0817e0e7","tid":439672,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"2017年07月24日13:31<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/07/24/f/f67096d4f99b75ce1916dfca0434260f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2Ff%2Ff67096d4f99b75ce1916dfca0434260f.jpg&h=eec260cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/07/24/8/815ab8267c9e92d71733069a0579556b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F8%2F815ab8267c9e92d71733069a0579556b.jpg&h=eddecf64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先至聲明，本文絕對無意冒犯任何人士。<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「唔怕生壞命，最怕改錯名」，可見一個名對於一個人嚟講係幾咁重要！事實上唔單止係人，就算係地方名都一重非常緊要，因為一覺唔留神，分分鐘鬧出笑話！最近就有網民發現日本有一個「多肥西公園」嘅地方，真係聽個名都知道重口味啦......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/07/24/3/34a8b06611d21975a4b84d6c8b9fbf4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F3%2F34a8b06611d21975a4b84d6c8b9fbf4c.jpg&h=f98f09f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/07/24/1/13590d2dad1b55c376e5afe3e4b08dfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F1%2F13590d2dad1b55c376e5afe3e4b08dfb.jpg&h=8444e9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/07/24/d/d4c8f8e00d0838129bad8c8beb2f9a93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2Fd%2Fd4c8f8e00d0838129bad8c8beb2f9a93.jpg&h=f2154b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「有圖有真相」，從告示牌可見，呢個公園的確叫「多肥西公園」，呢個咁特別嘅嘅公園位於日本四國東北嘅高松市，從網上圖片可見，呢個公園同普同公園冇咩分別，一樣係有韆鞦、滑梯、玩具馬等，比較特別嘅地方係呢個公園唔好話「肥西」，就連人影都似乎唔多個。<br />\n<br />\n下次如果大家再去日本旅遊，不妨 mark 低呢個地方，睇下會唔會見到好多「肥西」？"},{"pid":"bfff6d0b904967bc222d803b48025d6ac6d9986c","tid":439672,"uid":137409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"Fun"},{"pid":"cb88306a6b5f0e731e5fcc851e9126c00e2d5cf9","tid":439672,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"多い肥ったビッチだった公園"},{"pid":"a091515236d089f2b21d52cace5b32587c6eaa66","tid":439672,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"因為佢係多肥下町囉"},{"pid":"11f6a371635bfd332c5ec10bd803bfb393e15189","tid":439672,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc4b0012b16c935c4f0b2b0d904b48ca4b3a02d2","tid":439672,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高登公海高登連登</blockquote><br />\n高登&gt;公海&gt;高登&gt;連登&gt;FB"},{"pid":"1f8c0e52eb0b1fdf59dadae0922bbbd7768c5d98","tid":439672,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"文化差異啫，咪好似肥西老母雞咁"},{"pid":"426906e0887d49644f5957707b884d5b804519e7","tid":439672,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"肥西老母雞"},{"pid":"9f3e8315d2d93d0e0cda91fd4cedc7790889c07c","tid":439672,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"十年前上高登又係呢個POST"},{"pid":"c50d484e34b186454e8515713f3e0e011c0c1301","tid":439672,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}